compare - Compare the lines of the given files. See implementation for comparison algorithms

Parameters:
ui - - Driver for UI generated input
expectedFile - - Baseline file that is expected to be the expected results
actualFile - - Source file whose lines are to be compared against the given baseline (expected) file
Throws:
DifferenceException - - When at least one line in the actual file does not match the pattern of the same line (by line number) in the baseline file
